  "response": "Opening a savings bank account with ICICI Bank typically takes around 30-45 minutes, provided you have all the necessary documents ready. The process involves:\n\n1. Document verification\n2. Form filling\n3. KYC (Know Your Customer) documentation\n4. Initial deposit submission\n\nYou'll need to provide:\n- Proof of identity (Aadhaar card, PAN card, etc.)\n- Proof of address\n- Passport-sized photographs\n- Filled application form\n\nYou can open an account:\n- Online through ICICI Bank's website\n- At a bank branch\n- Through a bank representative\n\nThe exact time may vary depending on branch workload and document verification process. If you apply online, the process might be quicker.",
